{"tid":1726640,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[正視聽］邊個無目的地破壞校園既一定唔係我手足","createTime":"2019-11-16T08:39:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-16T18:15:42.000Z","uid":9394,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"19d14f265baeb1a7e462495d1a0b898ebeb2ff36","tid":1726640,"uid":9394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T08:39:55.000Z","msg":"我唔係講緊做文宣/ust手足爆校長府果啲<br />\n都唔無講緊爆藍店<br />\n我係講緊<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">破壞對場運動無幫助 純粹發洩果啲</span><br />\n呢幾日中大 理大 都比人無意義咁破壞 <br />\n大學保健處（診所）圖書館都爛曬<br />\n呢種破壞係對全運動<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">亳無幫助</span><br />\n我懷疑係有鬼亂咁破壞 分化學生vs外來示威者<br />\n所以我希望係呢度講清楚 <br />\n如果有示威者亳無目的咁破壞<br />\n請大家勸阻<br />\n示威者同暴徒真係一線之差"},{"pid":"a17ba445b1a879ff4b639174c26fe92a252d924d","tid":1726640,"uid":120915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T15:37:36.000Z","msg":"Ching係咪想share遲啲YouTube應該有 不過可以tg send俾你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />爆咗po覆你唔到"},{"pid":"09972da0b14800f5422d35dd33fb6ada946e0b7e","tid":1726640,"uid":9394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a17ba445b1a879ff4b639174c26fe92a252d924d","tid":1726640,"uid":120915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T15:37:36.000Z","msg":"Ching係咪想share遲啲YouTube應該有 不過可以tg send俾你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />爆咗po覆你唔到"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T17:27:04.000Z","msg":"唔該手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n[member］<a href=\"https://t.me/Kirinlamon[/member]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FKirinlamon%5B%2Fmember%5D&d=x8osXdNjm17U7TcHCf5EXh1%2FCJV8QLW4B9aSVLpa5FM%3D&h=3a34b03f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/Kirinlamon[/member]</a>"},{"pid":"28a83219945e27e7c16d4b218ad274f8e04a0e39","tid":1726640,"uid":120915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"09972da0b14800f5422d35dd33fb6ada946e0b7e","tid":1726640,"uid":9394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"